The Latvian Judo Federation president Raymond Rublovskis did not arrive at Rio de Janeiro, at least during the Latvian athletes competitions, though it was planned; the Latvian Canoe Federation currently has no president; the weightlifting Latvian society is still experiencing conflicts and its athletic international competitions apply to the Latvian Olympic Committee.
